exception handelling keywords:
===============================
try      -   to maintain the risky code 
catch    -   to handle the exception (handle the exception or convert system error messages into user friendly error messages and returnt o the UI)
finally  -   this is default block, which maintains the logic for cleanup the connection objects/ cleanup the streams 
throws   -   delegate the exceptipon handelling responsibility to the caller 
throw    -   this is used to manually throw the exception  
==========================================================


methods to print exception information
======================================
printStackTrace(); => this method gives complete information about exception

